<h1>Riots, Strikes and 200,000 Toxic Products</h1>
<p><b>Hong Kong, July 10, 2014</b> - AsiaInspection, a leading global provider of quality control services for businesses importing from Asia, Africa, Southern Europe and Latin America, today announces its 2014 Q2 Barometer, a quarterly synopsis on outsourced manufacturing and the quality control services industry.</p>

